Mercedes-Benz Credit Corp is issuing a 100mln dlr eurobond due June 25, 1992 paying 8-1/4 pct and pricedat 100-1/2 pct, lead manager Deutsche Bank Capital Marketssaid.    The non-callable bond is available in denominations of1,000 and 10,000 dlrs and will be listed in Luxembourg. Theselling concession is 1-1/4 pct while management andunderwriting combined pays 5/8 pct.    The payment date is June 25. REUTER&#3;